{"tid":462832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實羊又好，狗又好","createTime":"2017-11-09T02:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T03:08:37.000Z","uid":135333,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f11d0920e84314077f51547e009ea1bda7e5f86b","tid":462832,"uid":135333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:29:12.000Z","msg":"我都覺得香港人好撚偽善，羊就得，狗就唔得，切左羊頭就無問題，切左狗頭都俾人批鬥<br />\n狗就係朋友，羊就係食物<br />\n羊唔可愛咩，根本就係d濕鳩香港人係度打飛機，以為自己係高尚人種，同大陸人有分別，但其實根本就係一撚樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人係偽君子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 羊係低賤過狗"},{"pid":"9f70d34e07da1fd3dd40b87c14265c3ffdbd68b4","tid":462832,"uid":135333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T02:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b263d683124b67e8cd17df5a5c3c561ca840e61d","tid":462832,"uid":135333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b035c467457c6b6d3877470f4791108f88f315","tid":462832,"uid":135390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得所有動物都好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我怕佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6061c0c0aeb00aa5ba6d14eee03585900eeb56","tid":462832,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:08:37.000Z","msg":"大陸仔睇法"}]}